; Coverage test for account.cc fn_any (L373-383).
; In balance context, any(expr) checks if any posting of the account
; matches the expression. Also exercises fn_all (L385-395).

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --limit "any(amount > 20)"
             $-30.00  Assets:Cash
              $30.00  Expenses:Gas
--------------------
                   0
end test
